title: Medieval Castle with Marc Morris (2003 - Complete Series)
description:
TV : Documentary : TV quality : English


Channel 4 History 6-part documentary featuring historian Marc Morris, who details the history of the British castle. Each episode details either an era of castle-building, what they were used for, and/or focuses more specifically on castle-building in a specific region of Britain.

This series played on Channel 4 in 2003, and has been replayed recently on Discovery Civilisation.

Enjoy and Seed!!
